animeDescription: A collaboration between Kemurikusa's TV series and Nissin. They promote the latter's Donbei Tsukimi Soba (moon-viewing soba) product after Wakaba finds several packages of them.
animeRelated: ['Nissin no Donbei x Kemono Friends', 'Kemurikusa (TV)', 'Nissin Men-nashi Donbei x Himote House']
